data.title: SESSION TALK WITH ROB AND PAT
data.description:
Rob Machado and Pat O'Connell have been traveling across Europe for Hurley's Rip My Shred Stick Tour. The guys managed to sneak in a free surf one afternoon at Hossegor, France. The beach brought back some fond (and not so fond) memories as you can tell from the video. 

Video: PK.
